[Desktop Entry]
Type=Application
Name=MCNF Mesh Boot Status
Comment=BOOT-STATUS-5 — opens the Workbench at the mesh bring-up status at login, so the boot handshake (Nebula → bus → etcd → peers) is front-and-centre. Exits silently when the mesh is already all-green (the applet chip suffices).
Exec=mde-workbench --boot-popup
Icon=magic-mesh
Terminal=false
NoDisplay=true
X-GNOME-Autostart-enabled=true
